            "body": "Some solutions are change the proxy server, but I think it's not server problem on logistic, and I try to set HOST_NAME in flask app's config but got all request 404, I fixed it by add my domain to the result of url_for as the paramter of redirect();\r\n\r\n```python\r\n    return redirect(config.myhostname+url_for('index'))\r\n# myhostname should prefix with protocal name such as http://\r\n``` \r\nI think this solution is bad, but it works.\r\n"
